      nnex sylancl 0z mptex eqeltri ax-1cn eqeltrd ad3antrrr divcnv eqid eqtr4d
      fvconst2g oveq12d climsub subid1 breqtrd fex vex coexg fss fveq2d breq12d
      fco rcla4cva adantll wfun ffun simpllr simpr fvco3 breqtrrd simplr syldan
      syl3anc suprub syl6breqr climsqz ex imdistanda eximdv ) ARJGUDZUEZUAUDZEU
